   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Harpaesis, foreman of the epoikion Adaiou, to Matreas, the most honored, greetings. If it seems good to you, send me then from the account of the Julii Theones, as payment for the building up of [    ] which is once more to be put in order, a hundred and twenty drachmas; and as payment for the cutting of the green fodder [   ] four hundred drachmas, for which I shall render an account, total 520 drachmas. Greetings, most honored. Year 20 of Antoninus Caesar the lord. Pachon 1. (2nd hd.) Give the 520 drachmas."</ab>
         </div>
